M|model-selection|Ask three questions before picking a model:
M|model-selection|1. **What is the output type?** (image / video / audio / text)
M|model-selection|2. **What is the primary use case?** (product shot / soc ad / animation / character / editorialâ€¦)
M|model-selection|3. **What constraints apply?** (speed needed / budget / need style control / need text in image / need brand consistencyâ€¦)
M|model-selection|Start here. These work for product shots, static ads, on-brand assets, character visuals, soc media posts.
M|model-selection|| Model | Best for | Notes |
M|model-selection||---|---|---|
M|model-selection|| **Nano Banana 2** | Fast, versatile generation | Default first choice for most image tasks |
M|model-selection|| **Nano Banana Pro** | On-brand assets needing quality bump | Use when Nano Banana 2 needs more fidelity |
M|model-selection|| **Seedream 5.0 Lite** | Fast iteration, broad use cases | Good balance of speed and quality |
M|model-selection|| **Seedream 4.5** | Quality product & lifestyle shots | Step up from 5.0 Lite for final outputs |
M|model-selection|| Need | Model(s) |
M|model-selection||---|---|
M|model-selection|| Editorial / inspiration aesthetic | Recraft v4, Higgsfield Soul, Reve |
M|model-selection|| On-brand with style control via prompt | Recraft v4 |
M|model-selection|| On-brand with style control via reference images | Ideogram v3, Reve |
M|model-selection|| Consistent brand style across assets | Flux 2, GPT Image 1.5 |
M|model-selection|| Character & mascot visuals | Ideogram Character, GPT Image 1.5 |
M|model-selection|| Fast visual iterations (speed > quality) | Grok Imagine Image, Flux 2 Klein, Nano Banana |
M|model-selection|| Vector / layout-ready output | Recraft v4 |
M|model-selection|| soc media post assembly | Any image model + Composer node |
M|model-selection|| Text-in-image (accurate typography) | GPT Image 1.5, Ideogram v3 |
M|model-selection|| Custom fine-tuned brand model | Contact Pletor team |
M|model-selection|```
