M|model-selection|| Model | Use |
M|model-selection||---|---|
M|model-selection|| **Veed Fabric 1.0** | Most popular. Works with video or still image â€” talking character |
M|model-selection|| **Hedra Character 3** | Strong for portrait-to-character animation |
M|model-selection|| **Kling 3.0** (via Lipsync node) | Integrated lipsync in Kling's video generation |
M|model-selection|**Lipsync works with both video and still images** â€” you can animate a static portrait photo into a speaking character.
M|model-selection|Use the gen Audio node for:
M|model-selection|- Voiceover / narration from script
M|model-selection|- Sound design
M|model-selection|Pletor curates audio models in the Audio Models library â€” select based on language, voice style, and tone needed.
M|model-selection|Pletor provides dedicated upscaling models for both images and video.
M|model-selection|**When to upscale:**
M|model-selection|- Add Upscale Image after any gen Image node in a final prd pl
M|model-selection|- Add Upscale Video when resolution matters for the distribution format
M|model-selection|Upscaling is almost always the last node in an image or video chain before output.
M|model-selection|Text Assistant nodes run LLMs for:
M|model-selection|- Prompt enhancement
M|model-selection|- Copy generation (headlines, CTAs, ad copy)
M|model-selection|- Translation / localization
M|model-selection|- Multi-input processing (combine user prompt + brand ctx)
M|model-selection|Pletor's text model library is in the Text Models section. For most use cases, the default model is appropriate. Upgrade to a more powerful model if you need complex reasoning or long-form output.
M|model-selection|| Task | Recommended |
M|model-selection||---|---|
M|model-selection|| Product shot, static ad | Nano Banana 2 |
M|model-selection|| On-brand lifestyle image | Nano Banana Pro or Seedream 4.5 |
M|model-selection|| Editorial / fashion aesthetic | Recraft v4 or Higgsfield Soul |
M|model-selection|| Text in image | GPT Image 1.5 or Ideogram v3 |
M|model-selection|| Character / mascot | Ideogram Character |
M|model-selection|| Fast prototyping | Grok Imagine Image or Nano Banana |
M|model-selection|| Product video from photo | Kling 3.0 |
M|model-selection|| Cinematic video | Veo 3.1 |
M|model-selection|| Animated illustration | Kling 2.5 or Hailuo 2.3 |
M|model-selection|| Talking character / lipsync | Kling 3.0 + Lipsync, or Veed Fabric |
M|model-selection|| Long UGC video | Sora 2 |
M|model-selection|| High volume video | Seedance 1.5 Pro or Kling 2.6 |
M|model-selection|| Edit existing video | Kling O3/O1 |